---
import TextLink from "@components/TextLink.astro";
import { resolvePath } from "@lib/utils";

type Props = {
  small?: boolean;
};

const { small } = Astro.props;
---

<div style={small ? "font-size: 0.875rem" : ""}>

<p>Who are we? </p>

We are Domain Name Plus, your strategic partner in navigating the digital landscape. We believe a domain name is far more than an address—it's the cornerstone of your online identity.

<p><TextLink href="https://Domain name.plus">Domain Name</TextLink> Plus.</p>

<p>What is a Domain Name? </p>
A domain name is your website's unique name and address on the internet. But at its core, it represents three critical pillars of your digital success:
Your Digital Brand Identity. It's the name customers remember, trust, and return to. A strong, concise domain name enhances brand recognition and user experience。
Your Foundation of Credibility. A professional and relevant domain name instantly establishes trust with your audience and search engines, signaling stability and authority.
Your Appreciating Digital Asset. A well-chosen domain name is not an expense; it's a strategic investment. Like prime real estate, it holds inherent value, drives targeted traffic, and can appreciate over time。

<p>Our Mission at Domain Name Plus</p>
We go beyond simply registering names. Our mission is to empower you to choose a domain that is short, memorable, brand-aligned, and optimized for long-term growth. We combine industry expertise with a client-centric approach to help you secure a digital asset that strengthens your brand and stands the test of time.

<p>Let's build your digital foundation together.</p>

<p>Domain Name Plus!</p>
</div>
